# GEMINI_API_KEY: Required for Gemini AI API calls (Prompt generation).
GEMINI_API_KEY="YOUR_GEMINI_API_KEY"

# APP_URL: The URL where this applet is hosted.
# AI Studio automatically injects this at runtime with the Cloud Run service URL.
# Used for self-referential links, OAuth callbacks, and API endpoints.
APP_URL="MY_APP_URL"


# --- Veo 3.1 Labs API (via Cloudflare Worker Proxy) ---
# The Cloudflare Worker handles all sensitive credentials server-side.
# Only the Worker URL is needed here (used at build time by the frontend).

# VEO_LABS_PROXY_URL: Cloudflare Worker URL for Labs API proxy
# Deploy cloudflare-worker/veo-labs-proxy.js first, then set the URL here.
# Example: https://veo-labs-proxy.your-subdomain.workers.dev
VEO_LABS_PROXY_URL=""

# The following credentials are set DIRECTLY in Cloudflare Worker Settings
# (Dashboard → Workers → veo-labs-proxy → Settings → Variables):
#   LABS_API_KEY          — Google Labs API key
#   LABS_PROJECT_ID       — Google Labs project UUID
#   LABS_ACCESS_TOKEN     — (Optional) Tạm thời sử dụng nếu không dùng Cookies
#
#   --- Cấu hình Google Cookies để vượt qua xác thực và reCAPTCHA ---
#   LABS_COOKIE_1PAPISID  — Value của cookie __Secure-1PAPISID
#   LABS_COOKIE_1PSID     — Value của cookie __Secure-1PSID
#   LABS_COOKIE_1PSIDCC   — Value của cookie __Secure-1PSIDCC
#   LABS_COOKIE_1PSIDTS   — Value của cookie __Secure-1PSIDTS
#   LABS_COOKIE_3PAPISID  — Value của cookie __Secure-3PAPISID
#   LABS_COOKIE_3PSID     — Value của cookie __Secure-3PSID
#   LABS_COOKIE_3PSIDCC   — Value của cookie __Secure-3PSIDCC
#   LABS_COOKIE_3PSIDTS   — Value của cookie __Secure-3PSIDTS
